**Create New Email Address**

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , click on **Client Portal**.
- Click on the **Menu** , then goto **Email Management**.
- Choose a domain from the drop down list named **Choose a domain to manage its email**.
- Click on the **Create email account** button >> Complete the form with desired account name and a corresponding password.

```diagram

```

**Delete Email Account**

 Customer can delete unwanted email accounts. To do that click on the **Delete**  button beside the email address want to delete under **Email Management**.

**Reset Email Account Password**

If a customer forgot their login password. Now they can reset the email account password from client portal. To do that go to **Menu** >> **Email Management**.

Click on the email account want to reset password. Write the new password under  POP/IMAP option and submit it. 

```diagram

```

**Email Forwarders **

Customer can setup email forwarders to forward emails to another email address. To do that go to **Menu** >> **Email Management**.

Click on the email account want to add forwards. Put the forwarder email address under  **Forwarders** option and submit it.

**Email Aliases**

Customer can setup email aliases to send a copy of  emails to another email address. To do that go to **Menu** >>** Email Management**.

Click on the email account want to add aliases. Put the alias email address under  **Aliases** option and submit it.

**Email Auto Responders**

Customer can setup email auto responders to to automatically send a reply, such as a "Thank you" or a "out of office" message. To do that go to **Menu** >> **Email Management**.

Click on the email account want to setup auto response. Complete the form with necessary details like the response subject, content and the expire date under the **Responders** option and submit the form.
